### Usage instructions:
### 1. Replace {{base_url}} with your application's actual URL
###    For local testing: http://localhost:8000
###    For Azure App Service: https://your-app-name.azurewebsites.net
### 
### 2. To simulate brute-force attack, execute requests from section 8
###    quickly one after another (more than 5 times in 5 minutes)
###
### 3. Each request generates logs that will be visible in Azure Monitor